<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV3">
<l>kuḻaṟkō valarmaṭap pāvaiyu maṇmaka ḷuntiruvu</l>
<l>niḻaṟpōl vaṉarkaṇṭu niṟkuṅkol mīḷuṅkol taṇṇantuḻā</l>
<l>yaḻaṟpō laṭuñcakka rattaṇṇal viṇṇōr toḻakkaṭavun</l>
<l>taḻaṟpōl ciṉattavap puḷḷiṉpiṉ pōṉa taṉineñcamē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Seeing those who are like [his] shadow, the youthful girl of the cowherds with flutes,</l>
<l>the lady earth and Śrī, will it stay, will it return? – [my] lonely heart that had gone</l>
<l>after that bird with fire-like anger that is driven, while the celestials worship,</l>
<l>by the Majesty with the discus deadly like fire, with cool tulsi.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
